
=======================
Nagios Operation Center
=======================

Installation in Splunk Indexer
------------------------------
Untar the application into ${SPLUNK_HOME}/etc/apps, and go to Setup page
into the application page.


Installation in Splunk HeavyForwarder
-------------------------------------
Untar the application into ${SPLUNK_HOME}/etc/apps. Edit (or create) the
file  ${SPLUNK_HOME}/etc/apps/NagiosOperationCenter/local/nagiosoc.conf,
con el siguiente contenido::

  [nagiosoc]
  path = /etc/nagios3/nagios.cfg


Where path is the path of the nagios config file.

